CR:

The proces was acording the planned and soon the weapons and habilities 
configuration was starting.





-----Mensaje original----- 
From: Super Cyclonus
Sent: Friday, August 05, 2011 6:27 AM
To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com
Subject: Re: MEdic Bay

As NIGHTSHIFT began his training of the young maximal a message came
in for NIGHTSHIFT requesting his presence. The coordinates came along
with the message.

At the same time small alarm bells went off on NIGHTLIGHT's CR chamber
which BUMP quickly shut off as he fed in a few commands. The systems
began to hum again as green lights once again appeared.

"It was nothing." BUMP said as he turned to look back at ELITA and
NIGHTSHIFT, "Remember she requested a fuzor form, they were created
because of a mistake in beast mode creation subroutines when their
ship crash landed. We just had to recreate that."

He glanced back at NIGHTLIGHT's CR chamber and nodded, "All is going
well. She should be done shortly." The CR chamber hummed along
pleasently, its timer continuing to count down.

(TAG)

Preston
